        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3547948232" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer3906255868886601862">Another brilliant book from Kirsten Fullmer, an absolute pro at cozy mysteries. As I said in another review all of the books in this series follow a similar vein but remain so special in their own right. They are wonderfully written and the characters are original and quirky in their own individual ways. The plot always seems to offer something unexpected and I have loved all the series so far. </span>

          </span>
        </div>


