      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Rachelle Steward" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Rachelle Steward" href="/user/show/89733237-rachelle-steward">Rachelle Steward</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Kindle Edition " href="/book/show/54775025-shadows-in-the-salon">review of another edition</a>


        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3668850632" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer16984714297913387723"><strong>Light hearted fun!</strong><br/><br/>Wonderfully sweet and charming these characters make you fall in love with them immediately. The small town cheerfully celebrating the holidays with their traditions. Friends who literally run to you to help in a crisis. Everyone has a task in the mission and does it well. These ladies are fierce, so watch out criminals! Romping good fun, all in all.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


