        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3642962425" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer14341326325884646748"><strong>2.5 I guess</strong><br/><br/>Quick light read, but don&apos;t go into it expecting a cozy--it really doesn&apos;t feel like one. It also feels a bit abbreviated. A number of things were skirted around and it doesn&apos;t feel complete in the end. A major concern is never dealt with and a project left hanging.</span>
  <span id="freeText14341326325884646748" style="display:none"><strong>2.5 I guess</strong><br /><br />Quick light read, but don't go into it expecting a cozy--it really doesn't feel like one. It also feels a bit abbreviated. A number of things were skirted around and it doesn't feel complete in the end. A major concern is never dealt with and a project left hanging.</span>
